Great tools for making PNG image looks good on IE &hellip;. , there is two files that need to be used to make it work
 iepngfix.htc
http://code.google.com/p/widgetfx/source/browse/widgetfx.org/iepngfix.htc
 iepngfix_tilebg.js
http://code.google.com/p/widgetfx/source/browse/widgetfx.org/iepngfix_tilebg.js?r=144
  Include iepngfix.htc on your css style file
*html img, *html #anydivid {
behavior: url(style/iepngfix.htc);
border:0;
padding:0; }

include this iepngfix_tilebg.js on you html header, it support for transparent image on background position and repeat.
